      <title>DCGAN</title>
      <link href="/2021/11/23/DCGAN/"/>
      <url>/2021/11/23/DCGAN/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="DCGAN的复现"><a href="#DCGAN的复现" class="headerlink" title="DCGAN的复现"></a>DCGAN的复现</h1><p>一般的神经网络模型的模板可以写为：</p><ol><li><p>导入相关包</p></li><li><p>定义一些超参数</p></li><li><p>数据处理并读取数据集</p></li><li><p>定义神经网络结构</p></li><li><p>训练网络</p><p>​                1.定义优化器和损失函数</p><p>​                2.循环训练</p><p>​                3.输出预测值</p><p>​                4.计算误差</p><p>​                5.清空上一步残余</p><p>​                6.误差反向传播</p><p>​                7.参数更新</p><p>6.测试</p></li></ol><p>一般分为几个py文件来写比较清晰，例如module.py、mydataset.py、utils.py(写一些处理函数，数据读取等)、train.py、predit.py的模板。</p><h2 id="自定义数据集"><a href="#自定义数据集" class="headerlink" title="自定义数据集"></a>自定义数据集</h2><p>此次复现的是读取动漫头像来生成动漫头像,</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">class MyDataSet(Dataset):</span><br><span class="line">    &quot;&quot;&quot;自定义数据集&quot;&quot;&quot;</span><br><span class="line">    def __init__(self, transform=None):     # 定义文件路径和文件图像的路径</span><br><span class="line">        self.path = &#x27;./faces&#x27;</span><br><span class="line">        self.img_path = os.listdir(self.path)</span><br><span class="line">        self.transform = transform</span><br><span class="line">    def __getitem__(self, item):           # 从文件中读取数据、数据的transform、返回数据</span><br><span class="line">        img_name = self.img_path[item]</span><br><span class="line">        img_item_path = os.path.join(self.path, img_name)</span><br><span class="line">        img = Image.open(img_item_path)</span><br><span class="line">        if self.transform is not None:</span><br><span class="line">            img = self.transform(img)</span><br><span class="line">        return img</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    def __len__(self):                     # 返回数据的总共个数</span><br><span class="line">        return len(self.img_path)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>在自定义好数据集后，要进行实例化并且要传入所需要的参数。之后就可以写Dataloader来以batch_size的个数来训练。</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">train_data = MyDataSet(transform=transforms.Compose([</span><br><span class="line">    transforms.Resize(64),</span><br><span class="line">    transforms.ToTensor(),</span><br><span class="line">    transforms.Normalize(mean=[0.485, 0.456, 0.406], std=[0.229, 0.224, 0.225])]</span><br><span class="line">))</span><br><span class="line">face_data = DataLoader(dataset=train_data, batch_size=Batch_size, shuffle=True)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="定义网络结构"><a href="#定义网络结构" class="headerlink" title="定义网络结构"></a>定义网络结构</h2><p>鉴别器的网络结构：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># 鉴别器</span><br><span class="line">class Discriminator(nn.Module):</span><br><span class="line">    def __init__(self):</span><br><span class="line">        super(Discriminator, self).__init__()</span><br><span class="line">        self.d_module = nn.Sequential(</span><br><span class="line">            # Image (3x64x64)</span><br><span class="line">            nn.Conv2d(in_channels=3, out_channels=128, kernel_size=4, stride=2, padding=1),</span><br><span class="line">            nn.LeakyReLU(0.2, inplace=True),</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">            # State (128x32x32)</span><br><span class="line">            nn.Conv2d(in_channels=128, out_channels=256, kernel_size=4, stride=2, padding=1),</span><br><span class="line">            nn.BatchNorm2d(256),</span><br><span class="line">            nn.LeakyReLU(0.2, inplace=True),</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">            # State (256x16x16)</span><br><span class="line">            nn.Conv2d(in_channels=256, out_channels=512, kernel_size=4, stride=2, padding=1),</span><br><span class="line">            nn.BatchNorm2d(512),</span><br><span class="line">            nn.LeakyReLU(0.2, inplace=True),</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">            # State (512x8x8)</span><br><span class="line">            nn.Conv2d(in_channels=512, out_channels=1024, kernel_size=4, stride=2, padding=1),</span><br><span class="line">            nn.BatchNorm2d(1024),</span><br><span class="line">            nn.LeakyReLU(0.2, inplace=True))</span><br><span class="line">        # outptut of main module --&gt; State (1024x4x4)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        self.output = nn.Sequential(</span><br><span class="line">            nn.Conv2d(in_channels=1024, out_channels=1, kernel_size=4, stride=1, padding=0),</span><br><span class="line">            # Output 1</span><br><span class="line">            nn.Sigmoid())</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    def forward(self, x):</span><br><span class="line">        x = self.d_module(x)</span><br><span class="line">        x = self.output(x)</span><br><span class="line">        return x</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>生成器的网络结构：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># 生成器</span><br><span class="line">class Generator(nn.Module):</span><br><span class="line">    def __init__(self, channels):</span><br><span class="line">        super(Generator, self).__init__()</span><br><span class="line">        self.g_module = nn.Sequential(</span><br><span class="line">            # Z latent vector 100</span><br><span class="line">            nn.ConvTranspose2d(in_channels=channels, out_channels=1024, kernel_size=4, stride=1, padding=0),</span><br><span class="line">            nn.BatchNorm2d(num_features=1024),</span><br><span class="line">            nn.ReLU(True),</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">            # State (1024x4x4)</span><br><span class="line">            nn.ConvTranspose2d(in_channels=1024, out_channels=512, kernel_size=4, stride=2, padding=1),</span><br><span class="line">            nn.BatchNorm2d(num_features=512),</span><br><span class="line">            nn.ReLU(True),</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">            # State (512x8x8)</span><br><span class="line">            nn.ConvTranspose2d(in_channels=512, out_channels=256, kernel_size=4, stride=2, padding=1),</span><br><span class="line">            nn.BatchNorm2d(num_features=256),</span><br><span class="line">            nn.ReLU(True),</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">            # State (256x16x16)</span><br><span class="line">            nn.ConvTranspose2d(in_channels=256, out_channels=128, kernel_size=4, stride=2, padding=1),</span><br><span class="line">            nn.BatchNorm2d(num_features=128),</span><br><span class="line">            nn.ReLU(True),</span><br><span class="line">            # State (128x32x32)</span><br><span class="line">            nn.ConvTranspose2d(in_channels=128, out_channels=3, kernel_size=4, stride=2, padding=1),</span><br><span class="line">        )</span><br><span class="line">        self.output = nn.Tanh()</span><br><span class="line">        # output of main module --&gt; Image (3x64x64)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    def forward(self, x):</span><br><span class="line">        x = self.g_module(x)</span><br><span class="line">        return self.output(x)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="定义网络，损失函数，优化函数"><a href="#定义网络，损失函数，优化函数" class="headerlink" title="定义网络，损失函数，优化函数"></a>定义网络，损失函数，优化函数</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">G_model = Generator(channels)</span><br><span class="line">D_model = Discriminator()</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">lossfunc = nn.BCELoss()</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">d_optimizer = torch.optim.Adam(D_model.parameters(), lr=LR, betas=(0.5, 0.999))</span><br><span class="line">g_optimizer = torch.optim.Adam(G_model.parameters(), lr=LR, betas=(0.5, 0.999))</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="训练部分"><a href="#训练部分" class="headerlink" title="训练部分"></a>训练部分</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br><span class="line">48</span><br><span class="line">49</span><br><span class="line">50</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">for epoch in range(num_epoch):</span><br><span class="line">    for i, img in enumerate(face_data):</span><br><span class="line">        num_img = img.size(0)</span><br><span class="line">        # 训练鉴别器</span><br><span class="line">        if use_gpu:</span><br><span class="line">            real_img = img.cuda()</span><br><span class="line">            real_label = torch.ones(num_img).cuda()  # 定义真实label为1</span><br><span class="line">            fake_label = torch.zeros(num_img).cuda()  # 定义假的label为0</span><br><span class="line">            z = torch.randn(num_img, channels, 1, 1).cuda()</span><br><span class="line">        # 计算真实图像的损失值</span><br><span class="line">        real_out = D_model(real_img)</span><br><span class="line">        # real_out = real_out.squeeze(-1)</span><br><span class="line">        d_loss_real = lossfunc(real_out.flatten(), real_label)</span><br><span class="line">        real_scores = real_out  # 真实图片放入判别器输出越接近1越好</span><br><span class="line">        # 计算伪造图像的损失值</span><br><span class="line">        fake_img = G_model(z)</span><br><span class="line">        fake_out = D_model(fake_img)</span><br><span class="line">        # fake_out = fake_out.squeeze(-1)</span><br><span class="line">        d_loss_fake = lossfunc(fake_out.flatten(), fake_label)</span><br><span class="line">        fake_scores = fake_out  # 假的图片放入判别器越接近0越好</span><br><span class="line">        # 优化</span><br><span class="line">        d_loss = d_loss_real + d_loss_fake  # 将真假图片的loss加起来</span><br><span class="line">        d_optimizer.zero_grad()</span><br><span class="line">        d_loss.backward()</span><br><span class="line">        d_optimizer.step()</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        # 训练生成器</span><br><span class="line">        if use_gpu:</span><br><span class="line">            z = torch.randn(num_img, channels, 1, 1).cuda()</span><br><span class="line">        fake_img = G_model(z)</span><br><span class="line">        output = D_model(fake_img)</span><br><span class="line">        # output = output.squeeze(-1)</span><br><span class="line">        g_loss = lossfunc(output.flatten(), real_label)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        # 优化</span><br><span class="line">        g_optimizer.zero_grad()</span><br><span class="line">        g_loss.backward()</span><br><span class="line">        g_optimizer.step()</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        if i % 20 == 0:</span><br><span class="line">            print(&#x27;Epoch [&#123;&#125;/&#123;&#125;], d_loss: &#123;:.6f&#125;, g_loss: &#123;:.6f&#125; &#x27;</span><br><span class="line">                  &#x27;D real: &#123;:.6f&#125;, D fake: &#123;:.6f&#125;&#x27;</span><br><span class="line">                  .format(epoch, num_epoch, d_loss.item(), g_loss.data.item(),</span><br><span class="line">                          real_scores.data.mean(), fake_scores.data.mean()))</span><br><span class="line">        # writer.add_scalar(&#x27;scores&#x27;, real_scores, epoch)</span><br><span class="line">        # writer.add_scalar(&#x27;scores&#x27;, fake_scores, epoch)</span><br><span class="line">        writer.add_scalar(&#x27;loss&#x27;, d_loss, epoch)</span><br><span class="line">        # writer.add_scalar(&#x27;loss&#x27;, g_loss, epoch)</span><br><span class="line">        torch.save(G_model.state_dict(), &quot;./weights/g_model-&#123;&#125;.pth&quot;.format(epoch))</span><br><span class="line">        torch.save(D_model.state_dict(), &quot;./weights/d_model-&#123;&#125;.pth&quot;.format(epoch))</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
